item.title: CVE-2021-21434|2024-08-03T18:16:22.278Z -- otrs%20ag -- survey
item.description: Survey administrator can craft a survey in such way that malicious code can be executed in the agent interface (i.e. another agent who wants to make changes in the survey). This issue affects: OTRS AG Survey 6.0.x version 6.0.20 and prior versions; 7.0.x version 7.0.19 and prior versions.
